<%- include('partials/head') %>
  <header class="mb-10 text-center">
    <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo-300/90">Closet QR</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">把衣櫃裝進 QR 裡</h1>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-lg text-slate-400">建立專屬衣櫃、上傳衣物照片與描述、掃碼即可瀏覽；還能用照片找出衣櫃裡最相近的單品。</p>
    <p class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-sm">
      <a href="/wardrobes" class="font-medium text-indigo-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-indigo-200 hover:underline">瀏覽全部衣櫃</a>
      <a href="/clothes" class="font-medium text-indigo-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-indigo-200 hover:underline">所有衣服</a>
    </p>
  </header>

  <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 shadow-xl backdrop-blur">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">建立新衣櫃</h2>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">建立後會顯示管理頁與 QR 碼。<strong class="font-medium text-slate-300">請務必將網址列含 <code class="rounded bg-white/10 px-1">?token=</code> 的完整連結加入書籤</strong>；遺失後無法從公開頁新增衣物。</p>
    <form action="/wardrobes" method="post" class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-end">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-300">衣櫃名稱（選填）</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" maxlength="80" placeholder="例如：主臥衣櫃"
          class="mt-1.5 w-full rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/80 px-4 py-2.5 text-white placeholder:text-slate-500 focus:border-indigo-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/40" />
      </div>
      <button type="submit"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-indigo-500 px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/25 transition hover:bg-indigo-400">
        建立衣櫃
      </button>
    </form>
  </section>

  <p class="mt-8 text-center text-xs text-slate-500">
    右上角可 <a href="/login" class="text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300">管理員登入</a>，登入後可編輯所有衣櫃（免 token）。技術棧：Express · MongoDB · Session · Tailwind CSS
  </p>
<%- include('partials/foot') %>
